The '''Squib Polyanarchy''' was the main governing body of [[Skor II]] and of the [[Squib/Legends|Squib]] species. It was made up of several independent communities under the nominal rule of a [[King/Legends|king]].<ref name="DB-Squib">{{DB|species|squib|Squib}}.</ref> The Squib king was [[Ebareebaveebeedee]] during the end of the [[Old Republic era]] and the beginning of the [[Imperial Era/Legends|Imperial Period]].<ref name="Hnn-Squibs Announce They're Going Nowhere.">{{HoloNetNewsWeb|47|regional/13314_2.html|Squibs Announce They're "Going Nowhere."}}</ref><ref name="Scavenger Hunt">[[Scavenger Hunt (adventure)|''Scavenger Hunt'']].</ref> The Squib Polyanarchy's relationship with the [[Squib Merchandising Consortium]], a Squib-wide corporation, is not known. The two may have been one and the same, they may have had different jurisdictions, or they may have overlapped.

